Class NonPositiveDimensionException

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Throwable
      • java.lang.Exception
        • java.lang.RuntimeException
          • shapes.InvalidShapeException
            • shapes.NonPositiveDimensionException
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class NonPositiveDimensionException
extends InvalidShapeException
    A RuntimeException indicating that a non-positive (negative or zero) value was provided as a dimension, which is not valid.
